comment.body:
@Alex-302 Hello, I was about to submit a new request, so I was reviewing the syntax to make sure I didn't make any mistakes again. 
And actually, I realized that your correction is, in the end, the same as my suggestion. So we should keep the first `pct|` right?

Because I saw that the latest stable version includes corelibs 1.20, which means that PCT is now fully supported, that's great news.
